NOTICE — third-party content & terms

This project does not host any media. Music videos are streamed from YouTube
via the YouTube IFrame Player API and remain the property of their respective
owners. Use of the embedded player and of YouTube content is subject to the
YouTube Terms of Service (https://www.youtube.com/t/terms) and the Google
Privacy Policy.

The optional data tooling in `scripts/` can use `youtubei.js`, an unofficial
client for YouTube's internal API. It is not affiliated with or endorsed by
YouTube/Google; prefer the official YouTube Data API v3 (set `YT_API_KEY`) for
production use. The MIT license above covers this project's own source code
only, not any third-party content or trademarks.
